  "text": "Genotyping of the study population Study participants were genotyped for K121Q (rs1044498) in exon 4 of the ENPP1 gene, which was shown to increase the risk of type 2 diabetes in whites in a recent meta-analysis [CITATION_1] . Genotyping was performed using the TaqMan assay, as previously described [CITATION_2] . The overall genotyping success rate was 100%, and re-screening of 3.2% of participants yielded 100% identical results.",
